subject: Palestinians
World Cup 2014 (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: Palestine advanced to the next round of Asia’s preliminary qualifying for the 2014 World Cup after tying Afghanistan, 1-1, in Al-Ram, West Bank, and winning by 3-1 over all.
